article.headline: House's 22 lead Rhode Island past Fairfield 93-80

images.name: Fairfield Stags vs. Rhode Island Rams: Full Highlights
images.caption: Fairfield Stags vs. Rhode Island Rams: Full Highlights

article.linkText: House's 22 lead Rhode Island past Fairfield 93-80
article.story: KINGSTON, R.I. -- — Jaden House's 22 points helped Rhode Island defeat Fairfield 93-80 on Thursday night. House shot 9 for 11, including 4 for 5 from beyond the arc for the Rams (2-0). David Fuchs scored 15 points while shooting 6 of 9 from the field and 3 for 6 from the line, and added 11 rebounds and three steals. Jeremy Foumena shot 5 of 10 from the field and 3 for 4 from the line to finish with 14 points, while adding six rebounds. Louis Bleechmore led the way for the Stags (0-2) with 24 points, 12 rebounds and three steals. Brycen Goodine added 22 points and two steals for Fairfield. In addition, Michael Rogan finished with 16 points. NEXT UP Up next for Rhode Island is a Tuesday matchup with Wagner at home, and Fairfield hosts Mount Saint Mary (NY) on Monday. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
